// Excel Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º AI AgentÍ∞Ä ÏùΩÍ∏∞ Ïâ¨Ïö¥ ÌÖçÏä§Ìä∏Î°ú Î≥ÄÌôò
const inputData = $input.first().json;
const excelData = inputData.data;
const rowCount = inputData.rowCount;
const clientName = inputData.clientName;
const analysisRequest = inputData.analysisRequest;

console.log(`=== Converting ${rowCount} rows for ${clientName} ===`);

if (!excelData || excelData.length === 0) {
  throw new Error('No data to process.');
}

// Ïπ¥ÌÖåÍ≥†Î¶¨Î≥ÑÎ°ú ÏßàÎ¨∏-ÎãµÎ≥Ä Í∑∏Î£πÌôî
const categories = {};
let validQACount = 0;

excelData.forEach((row, index) => {
  const category = row.Type || row.type || 'General';
  const question = row.Question || row.question || '';
  const feedback = row.Feedback || row.feedback || row.Answer || '';
  const id = row.ID || row.id || index + 1;

  if (!categories[category]) {
    categories[category] = [];
  }

  if (question && feedback) {
    categories[category].push({
      id: id,
      question: question,
      feedback: feedback
    });
    validQACount++;
  }
});

console.log('Valid Q&A pairs:', validQACount);
console.log('Categories:', Object.keys(categories));

if (validQACount === 0) {
  throw new Error('No valid Q&A pairs found. Check Excel structure.');
}

// Íµ¨Ï°∞ÌôîÎêú ÌÖçÏä§Ìä∏ ÏÉùÏÑ±
let formattedContent = '=== DISCOVERY QUESTIONNAIRE ANALYSIS ===\n\n';
formattedContent += `Client: ${clientName}\n`;
formattedContent += `Total Questions: ${validQACount}\n`;
formattedContent += `Categories: ${Object.keys(categories).join(', ')}\n\n`;

formattedContent += '=== DETAILED RESPONSES BY CATEGORY ===\n\n';

Object.keys(categories).forEach(category => {
  const items = categories[category];
  formattedContent += `## ${category.toUpperCase()} (${items.length} items)\n\n`;

  items.forEach(item => {
    formattedContent += `Q${item.id}: ${item.question}\n`;
    formattedContent += `A: ${item.feedback}\n\n`;
  });

  formattedContent += '\n';
});

console.log('Formatted content length:', formattedContent.length);

// AI AgentÍ∞Ä ÏÇ¨Ïö©Ìï† Ïª®ÌÖçÏä§Ìä∏
const context = {
  clientName: clientName,
  analysisRequest: analysisRequest,
  rowCount: validQACount,
  categories: Object.keys(categories),
  formattedContent: formattedContent,
  rawData: excelData,
  timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
};

console.log('‚úÖ Context prepared');

return [{ json: context }];

// Format for AI Agent ÎÖ∏ÎìúÏóêÏÑú Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Í∞ÄÏ†∏Ïò§Í∏∞
const formatNodeOutput = $('Format for AI Agent').first();

if (!formatNodeOutput || !formatNodeOutput.json) {
  return 'Error: Format for AI Agent node output not found';
}

const discoveryData = formatNodeOutput.json;

console.log('=== Tool: Get Discovery Data Called ===');
console.log('Available data keys:', Object.keys(discoveryData));

const requestedCategory = $input.item.json.category || '';
console.log('Requested category:', requestedCategory || 'ALL DATA');

// formattedContent ÌôïÏù∏
if (!discoveryData.formattedContent) {
  return 'Error: No formatted content available';
}

let result = '';

if (requestedCategory && requestedCategory.trim() !== '') {
  // ÌäπÏ†ï Ïπ¥ÌÖåÍ≥†Î¶¨Îßå ÏöîÏ≤≠Ìïú Í≤ΩÏö∞
  const lines = discoveryData.formattedContent.split('\n');
  let inCategory = false;
  let categoryContent = '';

  lines.forEach(line => {
    // Ïπ¥ÌÖåÍ≥†Î¶¨ ÏãúÏûë ÌôïÏù∏
    if (line.includes(`## ${requestedCategory.toUpperCase()}`)) {
      inCategory = true;
      categoryContent += line + '\n';
    } else if (line.startsWith('## ') && inCategory) {
      // Îã§Î•∏ Ïπ¥ÌÖåÍ≥†Î¶¨ ÏãúÏûëÌïòÎ©¥ Ï¢ÖÎ£å
      inCategory = false;
    } else if (inCategory) {
      categoryContent += line + '\n';
    }
  });

  if (categoryContent) {
    result = categoryContent.trim();
    console.log(`Returned category: ${requestedCategory}, length: ${result.length} chars`);
  } else {
    // Ïπ¥ÌÖåÍ≥†Î¶¨Î•º Ï∞æÏßÄ Î™ªÌïú Í≤ΩÏö∞
    const availableCategories = discoveryData.categories.join(', ');
    result = `Category "${requestedCategory}" not found.\n\nAvailable categories:\n${availableCategories}`;
    console.log('Category not found. Available:', availableCategories);
  }
} else {
  // Ï†ÑÏ≤¥ Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Î∞òÌôò
  result = discoveryData.formattedContent;
  console.log(`Returned all data, length: ${result.length} chars`);
}

// ToolÏùÄ Î¨∏ÏûêÏó¥ÏùÑ ÏßÅÏ†ë Î∞òÌôòÌï¥Ïïº Ìï®
return result;

const agentOutput = $input.first().json.output || $input.first().json.text || '';
const context = $('Format for AI Agent').first().json;

const validations = {
  hasContent: agentOutput.length > 200,
  hasBRD: agentOutput.toLowerCase().includes('business goal'),
